<h2>Sales Tax</h2>

elsa+sam is located in Oregon; therefore, we charge no sales tax.

<h2>Shipping &amp; Returns</h2>

All items are shipped via USPS Priority mail, unless otherwise requested and available. Shipping costs include insurance to make sure pieces arrive safely and in one piece. Please allow 1-2 weeks for normal delivery. Occasionally items may be oversold; in those cases we will ship backorder items once we receive them, or we will have items shipped directly from the warehouse. Sometimes items ordered together may not be shipped together, in which case we will contact you right away.

If items are damaged during shipping, please contact us within 10 days of receipt. If the item is replaceable, we will send out a replacement. If it is no longer available, you will receive full a refund of the item.

<strong>We do ship internationally</strong>. Rates vary by country. Please send us an email that includes your full shipping address at: <a href="mailto:info@elsasam.com">info@elsasam.com</a> and we will get back to you as quickly as possible.

<h2>Return Policy</h2>

Merchandise purchased from elsasam.com may be returned for credit or exchange within 14 days of purchase if in original condition and packaging and is accompanied with receipt. Store credit is valid for one year from date of issue. Shipping costs will not be refunded or credited. All costs for return shipment are the responsibility of the customer. <a href="/contact/">Click here</a> to contact us to initiate the return process.

